<urn:geoff:content:blog/2026-05-07-cpx-store-solid-transport.md> <https://schema.org/description> "Solid pods give users data sovereignty. CPX Store gives applications reactive state. The new SolidTransport bridges them — the collab plugin's SyncTransport interface, pointed at a pod resource, with W3C Solid Notifications for real-time updates." .
<urn:geoff:content:blog/2026-05-07-cpx-store-solid-transport.md> <https://schema.org/datePublished> "2026-05-07"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<urn:geoff:content:blog/2026-05-07-cpx-store-solid-transport.md> <https://schema.org/name> "CPX Store as a Reactive State Layer for Solid Pod Applications" .
<urn:geoff:content:blog/2026-05-07-agentic-sparql.md> <https://schema.org/isPartOf> <urn:geoff:content:blog/index.md> .
