<urn:geoff:content:blog/2026-05-07-agentic-sparql.md> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://schema.org/BlogPosting> .
<urn:geoff:content:blog/2026-05-07-agentic-sparql.md> <https://schema.org/description> "Geoff sites can now expose their RDF knowledge graph to AI agents via MCP manifests and a WASM SPARQL engine. Zero server cost, zero API to maintain — agents download the engine and data, then query locally." .
<urn:geoff:content:blog/2026-05-07-agentic-sparql.md> <https://schema.org/datePublished> "2026-05-07"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<urn:geoff:content:blog/2026-05-07-agentic-sparql.md> <https://schema.org/name> "Every Geoff Site Is Now an AI-Queryable Knowledge Base" .
<urn:geoff:content:blog/2026-05-03-rhds-case-study.md> <https://schema.org/about> "Static site generators" .
