<urn:geoff:content:blog/2026-04-23-cpx-store-scales-up.md> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://schema.org/BlogPosting> .
<urn:geoff:content:blog/2026-04-23-cpx-store-scales-up.md> <https://schema.org/description> "CPX Store started as a 162-line reactive Web Component. A plugin architecture, signal-inspired reactivity, microtask batching, pluggable collaboration transport, and a headless core for server-side rendering turn it into a state management system that runs anywhere JavaScript runs — without adding a single framework dependency." .
<urn:geoff:content:blog/2026-04-23-cpx-store-scales-up.md> <https://schema.org/datePublished> "2026-04-23"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<urn:geoff:content:blog/2026-04-23-cpx-store-scales-up.md> <https://schema.org/name> "From 162 Lines to IDE Scale: How CPX Store Grew Up" .
